lass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n約下出黎 人多/過馬路試下 有抗拒即係未得<br />\n（冇抗拒都唔代表得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） or 傾多d曖昧野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">雖然你好似假膠</span>"},{"pid":"b08fc535673f637b44eda020b60c5b22a55bfc6e","tid":126220,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解啲仆街仲可以幫俾綠帽人戴嘅人講說話？</blockquote><br />\n果個post我覺得就算樓主幾肥都唔係派帽理由<br />\n平時笑肥婆只係抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4de4b9ab367a3092492abecb84600533571043","tid":126220,"uid":83757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"點樣可以重新相信一個傷害過你嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b799715aa5f56c1997a880006a49208d6cb4486","tid":126220,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"天生太童顏又唔靚仔可以點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0dee82854eb18fdfbde95034902a5848432875","tid":126220,"uid":55652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一次拍 拍左一個月 女友無啦啦攞起張相問我邊個黎，只係一張公仔畫 ，話好頹 點算好 驚到hihi 已經解釋哂 佢又話自己問題 明明果張只係我同學黎"},{"pid":"c41ce42d1af07cd3f1f171dd80dc262d5c38e3d6","tid":126220,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣可以重新相信一個傷害過你嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要睇咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同你接受程度<br />\n第三者問題好易只係令佢隱藏得更深<br />\n同埋代表佢未玩夠"},{"pid":"edcc76ab2caa063c59c77309ba360abc4ef1501d","tid":126220,"uid":45705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"男朋友因為放唔低ex要同我分手 我可以點做 想等佢 想復合"},{"pid":"003fd433f619920883782dc98c2ad91c8c8cfee8","tid":126220,"uid":83757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點樣可以重新相信一個傷害過你嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要睇咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同你接受程度<br />\n第三者問題好易只係令佢隱藏得更深<br />\n同埋代表佢未玩夠</blockquote><br />\n簡短啲黎講，係佢一開頭當我玩具咁玩，過左一段時間我死心嘅時候，佢好認真咁話要同我發展，叫我信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903060d3cc34583caac17cf9a1f668f0d9409e24","tid":126220,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友因為放唔低ex要同我分手 我可以點做 想等佢 想復合</blockquote><br />\n佢擺明唔鍾意你啦 你問十個 十個都係咁答你<br />\n你咁樣等 最後等到佢都唔會珍惜你"},{"pid":"6d95e92865659ca0420bf7d3a41cef900cac093f","tid":126220,"uid":52285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:17:07.000Z","msg":"同個男仔一齊去日本，幾日同一個間房都冇事發生，佢係咪冇可能會中意我？<br />\n利申 真絲"},{"pid":"4d8851d61169388db4c3ed4f4c52515c2eb7f2f6","tid":126220,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣可以重新相信一個傷害過你嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要睇咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同你接受程度<br />\n第三者問題好易只係令佢隱藏得更深<br />\n同埋代表佢未玩夠</blockquote><br />\n簡短啲黎講，係佢一開頭當我玩具咁玩，過左一段時間我死心嘅時候，佢好認真咁話要同我發展，叫我信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開頭個動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d0a9431213c43ba91199484ee8fe62baf02316","tid":126220,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:18:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6656148ec00e835fe36d7d97ceeb243e17854514","tid":126220,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ca55d48accd96c2de21f5581d1727171e9e7c3c","tid":126220,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同個男仔一齊去日本，幾日同一個間房都冇事發生，佢係咪冇可能會中意我？<br />\n利申 真絲</blockquote><br />\n好難講 太多原因啦 實有既"},{"pid":"c703ee2433e121049876d9ab2f225b39d4f3c27d","tid":126220,"uid":83757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣可以重新相信一個傷害過你嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要睇咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同你接受程度<br />\n第三者問題好易只係令佢隱藏得更深<br />\n同埋代表佢未玩夠</blockquote><br />\n簡短啲黎講，係佢一開頭當我玩具咁玩，過左一段時間我死心嘅時候，佢好認真咁話要同我發展，叫我信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開頭個動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好想信佢，但真係有心無力，好辛苦<br />\n可唔可以教我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲屌鳩我成日提返以前嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry 我當唔到粉筆字咁抹走"},{"pid":"d55cf6c10c67e3ff4d844307af11f529b42841bd","tid":126220,"uid":52285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同個男仔一齊去日本，幾日同一個間房都冇事發